<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family: sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
    <h2>You've been invited to <%= @event.name %></h2>
    <p><%= @inviter.username %> has invited you to join their event on CatHerder.</p>
    <p>Make a free account to manage this invite and be able to create your own events.</p>
    <a href="<%= @app_url %>/login?mode=signup&contactType=email&email=<%= CGI.escape(@email) %>"
       style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 16px; padding: 12px 24px; background: #0097a7; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
      Create your free account
    </a>
  </body>
</html>
